Invocation Name: appointment maker
des: Customers can create, cancel, and reschedule, appointments with participating businesses. Only available appointments for businesses that have set up a portal on backofficescheduler.com are presented as choices and businesses may configure appointments to be made automatically or requested and then approved and scheduled later.
